org.smartregister.anc.library.repository

Class ContactTasksRepositoryHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • BaseRepository
      • org.smartregister.anc.library.repository.ContactTasksRepositoryHelper

  • public class ContactTasksRepositoryHelper
extends BaseRepository
    This class providers helper functions to perform any CRUD functions on the ANC Tasks. This tasks are mainly created from the ANC Tests. They include test that weren't done & all ordered tests.
